Mustang Two Four,<br><br>
If you land somewhere, I've got you covered. Though you might be just a grease pencil dot on a battle map somewhere, those dots were always brothers to me, one, five, ten, fifty, it mattered not. Funny thing about those dots, they all looked the same. When the map was full, watch out!<br><br>
You are a very generous man. You give of yourself constantly. Maybe it is now time for you to accept some of what is unconditionally offered.<br><br>
Maybe you have already landed, and just don't know it? It is often that way with me, and, can I fly high! Mostly I just bounce to a hard landing!<br><br>
The present is real, and that's where we're all at!<br><br>
Detonate Zulu
